p: The HPLC-Triple TOF-MS/MS data were processed by MarkerView 1.2.1 software (AB Sciex, USA), the characteristic peaks were inferred through comparing MS/MS fragment ions using PeakView1.2 (AB Sciex, USA), retention time ( tR) and mass data (m/z) pairs with standard compounds and online resources CNKI, Pubmed, SciFinder, HMDB.
